"{\"uid\": \"thedailybeast.com-convicted-child-rapist-to-compete-in-olympics-beach-volleyball\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Publisher & CEO  A convicted child rapist and registered sex offender was booed by spectators as he competed in beach volleyball at the Olympic Games on Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steven van de Velde, a Dutch beach volleyball player on a team ranked 10th in the world, was sentenced to four years in prison in 2016 after pleading guilty to raping a 12-year-old schoolgirl he met on Facebook.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9990566884273636, \"rank\": 0.0009442022496752208, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 185, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9354676949631726, \"rank\": 0.05689298226374607, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde was 19 in 2014 when he traveled from Amsterdam to England, drank Baileys Irish Cream Liqueur with the girl and raped her.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"score\": 0.9999999999959073, \"rank\": 2.328321123028202e-12, \"text\": \"Amsterdam\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9962875992196814, \"rank\": 0.0032813460026593732, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baileys_Irish_Cream\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Baileys Irish Cream\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baileys_Irish_Cream\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baileys_Irish_Cream\"}, {\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liqueur\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Liqueur\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liqueur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liqueur\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Sunday, just eight years later and still listed on the UK's sex offenders registry, van de Velde stepped onto thespecial sandof the Olympic beach volleyball court in the shadow of the Eiffel Tower to represent the Netherlands in a first-round match against Italy.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999991058170413, \"rank\": 8.941737631917551e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 598, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9990566884273636, \"rank\": 0.0009442022496752208, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9981702694447824, \"rank\": 0.001833032615625374, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.959509448460552, \"rank\": 0.04217216396083666, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was booed - and cheered - by the crowed when he was introduced.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He and his teammate, Matthew Immers, were defeated 2-1 by Italy and will play again against Chile on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.959509448460552, \"rank\": 0.04217216396083666, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.683742777368983, \"rank\": 0.462233545282362, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde (right) is being kept away from the Olympic Village and not is allowed to speak to the media.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3883351841992974e-20, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch Olympic Committee has insisted he is not a pedophile despite his conviction for raping a 12-year-old.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3872179058447294e-18, \"text\": \"Dutch Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What's in the past is in the past,\\\"van de Veld's teammate Immers told reporters, according to Reuters.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.046629954217952e-14, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He had his punishment and now he is really kind.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me it is an example that (he) grew and learnt a lot from it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Netherlands team press officer John van Vliet also told Reuters, \\\"It's something that should not be brought up through sports in a tournament that he qualified for... we have a person who has been convicted, who did his sentence and did everything afterwards that he can do to compete again.\\\"\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1400, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9995546675513626, \"rank\": 0.0004455100729442576, \"text\": \"The Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 1404, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Netherlands team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1460, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.046629954217952e-14, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde, now 29, was only caught because he had not used birth control and told the girl to get a morning-after-pill from a family planning clinic, which notified her family and police because of her age.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After being extradited from the Netherlands, van de Velde pleaded guilty to three counts of raping a child.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1941, \"end\": 1952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9981702694447824, \"rank\": 0.001833032615625374, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 1954, \"end\": 1966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9990566884273636, \"rank\": 0.0009442022496752208, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British judge admonished him: \\\"Your hopes of representing your country now lie as a shattered dream.\\\"\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2022, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9997252883720058, \"rank\": 0.00027441734454872337, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His lawyer said: \\\"He's lost a stellar sporting career\\u2026 it's plainly a career end for him.\\\"\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde served one year in a British prison before being transferred to the Netherlands, where he served another month and was released in 2017 because of more lenient Dutch underage sex laws.\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2250, \"end\": 2257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9997252883720058, \"rank\": 0.00027441734454872337, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9981702694447824, \"rank\": 0.001833032615625374, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9354676949631726, \"rank\": 0.05689298226374607, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Italian team of Adrian Ignacio Carambula Raurich (left) and Alex Ranghieri (right) celebrated a popular victory after winning 2-1.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2419, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.7746138646120017, \"rank\": 0.2759149025352936, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2442, \"end\": 2449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nacho_Varga\", \"score\": 0.7566189655820782, \"rank\": 0.3216692225403292, \"text\": \"Ignacio\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nacho_Varga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nacho_Varga\"}, {\"begin\": 2479, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ranghieri\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Ranghieri\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ranghieri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ranghieri\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon release from prison, van de Velde tried to defend himself.\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2577, \"end\": 2589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9990566884273636, \"rank\": 0.0009442022496752208, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone wants to be liked, everyone wants to be respected, and with something like this on your record, it's difficult,\\\" he said in a Dutch TV interview.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2751, \"end\": 2756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9354676949631726, \"rank\": 0.05689298226374607, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not reverse it, so I have to carry the consequences.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the biggest mistake of my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In another newspaper interview, he said: \\\"I have been branded as a sex monster, as a pedophile.\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That I am not-really not.\\\"\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Dutch national champion, van de Velde has pursued a pro beach volleyball career and played in international tournaments since being freed.\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2996, \"end\": 3001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9354676949631726, \"rank\": 0.05689298226374607, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 3021, \"end\": 3033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9990566884273636, \"rank\": 0.0009442022496752208, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 3052, \"end\": 3068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.325254210246476e-18, \"text\": \"beach volleyball\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But his selection as an Olympian has been heavily criticized by survivor groups.\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3159, \"end\": 3167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 6.8004140946908e-12, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beach volleyball takes place in a specially built stadium in front of the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris 2024 Olympics - Beach Volleyball - Women's Preliminary Phase - Pool A - Italy vs Spain (Gottardi/Menegatti vs Liliana/Paula) - Eiffel Tower Stadium, Paris, France - July 28, 2024.\\\\nGeneral view of t. REUTERS/Esa Alexander\\\"  The Dutch Olympic Committee stood by its decision to include him on the team and explained that van de Velde would not live in the Olympic Village or speak with the media.\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7688979605985605, \"rank\": 0.3005307591615871, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3429, \"end\": 3434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Hitler\", \"score\": 0.9762965487009945, \"rank\": 0.024278946115886827, \"text\": \"Paula\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Hitler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Hitler\"}, {\"begin\": 3460, \"end\": 3465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.471837802011146e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3467, \"end\": 3473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9457490852903545, \"rank\