idivism.\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde has consistently remained transparent about the case which he refers to as the most significant misstep of his life.\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He deeply regrets the consequences of his actions for those involved.\", \"from\": 4361, \"to\": 4430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been open about the personal transformation he has undergone as a result.\\\"\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde has been married to a German beach volleyball player since 2022 and they have a 2-year-old son.\", \"from\": 4514, \"to\": 4622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4549, \"end\": 4555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9752290311004991, \"rank\": 0.02103237161515396, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When van de Velde looks in the mirror now, he sees a mature and happy man, married and the father of a beautiful son,\\\" the Dutch Volleyball Association said on its website.\", \"from\": 4624, \"to\": 4797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4630, \"end\": 4642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9990566884273636, \"rank\": 0.0009442022496752208, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 4748, \"end\": 4776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nederlandse_Volleybalbond\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dutch Volleyball Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nederlandse_Volleybalbond\", \"dbpedia\": \"htt